metadata.description: The exclusive club of blockchain and artificial intelligence, where your NFT is the membership pass . Every member gets investment and business opportunities with our corporate network . The Metaverse DOMUS is borning, with an independent financial system, where the exchange currency are the crypto coins already present and the Domus Coin. The correlation between physical and digital world is so linked that both are necessary. Every object , building, contract in the world will be registered on the blockchain of the metaverse DOMUS. Transactions, properties, investments are safe and approved in both realities. The club meets once a year to plan innovative projects working on or investing in. The first global community of technology and innovation, work together to create significant changes in the industry. Each member of the club has the opportunity to record the own company on our blockchain to always be a step forward to competitors. WE ARE AGAINST THE BANKING AND INSURANCE SYSTEM!
